data.description: This beautiful 3 bedroom 3 bathroom nestled in the quiet community of Westwind.  Come home from a long a day at work and you're ready to unwind, as soon as you walk in you are welcomed by the inviting view of your pool and hot tub, your bedroom is to the left of the front door.   You make your way, get into your bathing suit, walk out of your bedroom doors into the pool area, where you already set the hot tub to turn on 15 minutes before you got home and jets are bubbling, the water is hot and your thought is, I'm home.  Can you see it?  Give me a call and we can get you there.
